name: boombox birthday card
description: ^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^ Say HAPPY BIRTHDAY to a friend with a talking boombox! Well, a fun, retro neon and grey drawing of one… Lovingly hand printed with a RISO GOCCO screen-printing machine in old London town, for your amusement and delight! All cards are A6 in size and come with an envelope inside a polybag. The envelope colour may vary from the picture, but a shade complimentary to the design will always be selected. Postage discounts are available for multiple purchases. If you are outside the UK, drop me an email for p+p costs. Thanks for looking – don’t forget to check back regularly – new and exciting products added all the time!!! ^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^
